2Fpakistan%2Fwatch-in-a-first-pakistan-army-admits-involvement-in-kargil-war%2Farticleshow%2F113150376.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Pakistan%20army%20chief%20General%20Asim%20Munir%20has%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20publicly%20acknowledged%20the%20military's%20involvement%20in%20the%20Kargil%20War%20during%20a%20Defence%20Day%20speech.%20This%20admission%20marks%20a%20departure%20from%20Pakistan's%20earlier%20stance%20of%20denying%20direct%20military%20participation%20and%20instead%20attributing%20it%20to%20'Kashmiri%20freedom%20fighters'.%20The%20Kargil%20War%20involved%20high-altitude%20combat%20and%20strategic%20infiltrations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20live%20in%20Korea%2C%20and%20I%20was%20hemorrhaging%20cash%20until%20I%20changed%20how%20I%20think%20about%20earning%20both%20American%20and%20Korean%20money%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-coach-get-more-out-money-living-abroad-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20and%20terms%20apply%20to%20offers%20listed%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20products%20and%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20make%20smart%20decisions%20with%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222844%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Krissi%20Driver%20in%20Gamcheon%20Culture%20Village%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66da14d81d8d2deb96b9a4a9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221422%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Krissi%20Driver.%3Cp%3EKrissi%20Driver%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAfter%20several%20years%20of%20teaching%20in%20Korea%2C%20I%20started%20earning%20money%20with%20U.S.%20companies%20on%20the%20side.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EFor%20several%20years%2C%20I%20didn't%20really%20know%20how%20to%20effectively%20manage%20having%20income%20in%20two%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMy%20money%20coach%20helped%20me%20change%20my%20mindset%20about%20how%20I%20manage%20multiple%20income%20streams.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20came%20to%20Korea%20in%202013%2C%20I%20arrived%20expecting%20to%20have%20one%20primary%20(and%20very%20modest)%20source%20of%20income%3A%20my%20teaching%20job%20at%20an%20after-school%20English%20academy%20for%20elementary-aged%20students.%20The%20problem%2C%20however%2C%20was%20that%20I%20was%20also%20saddled%20with%20%2460%2C000%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fstudent-loans%2Fbest-private-student-loans%5C%22%3Estudent%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Out%20of%20necessity%2C%20I%20sent%20most%20of%20my%20salary%20back%20to%20my%20U.S.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-banks%5C%22%3Ebank%20account%3C%2Fa%3E%20every%20month%20to%20fulfill%20my%20monthly%20loan%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20living%20in%20Korea%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20I%20found%20a%20way%20to%20supplement%20my%20income%3A%20freelance%20writing%20and%20working%20as%20an%20editor%20for%20a%20small%20boutique%20content%20marketing%20agency.%20Suddenly%2C%20I%20was%20earning%20money%20in%20the%20U.S.%20again.%20It%20wasn't%20much%20in%20the%20early%20days%2C%20but%20it%20was%20helpful%20for%20adding%20to%20my%20loan%20payments%20or%20buying%20and%20shipping%20things%20I%20couldn't%20get%20locally%2C%20like%20deodorant%2C%20my%20preferred%20brand%20of%20American%20toothpaste%2C%20or%20candles%20and%20oil%20diffusers%20in%20my%20favorite%20scents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20struggled%20with%20financial%20responsibility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20multiple%20streams%20of%20income%20came%20into%20different%20bank%20accounts%20in%20two%20countries%2C%20I%20was%20rarely%20a%20good%20steward%20of%20my%20earnings.%20Though%20I%20eventually%20managed%20to%20pay%20off%20%2460%2C000%20in%20student%20loans%2011%20years%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20living%20in%20Korea%2C%20I%20find%20myself%20falling%20into%20the%20habit%20of%20buying%20on%20credit%20and%20rolling%20over%20a%20balance%2C%20making%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcredit-score%2Fwhat-is-a-credit-score%5C%22%3Ecredit%20score%3C%2Fa%3E%20fluctuate%20and%20my%20blood%20pressure%20incrementally%20spike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20times%2C%20I%20would%20simply%20overspend%20in%20Korea%20and%20have%20digital%20dust%20bunnies%20left%20in%20my%20bank%20account%20before%20my%20next%20payday.%20To%20offset%20my%20sudden%20penniless%20circumstances%2C%20I%20would%20pull%20cash%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fatm-withdrawal-limits%5C%22%3EATM%20withdrawals%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20either%20money%20I'd%20sent%20home%20from%20my%20Korean%20salary%20or%20money%20I'd%20earned%20from%20writing%20%E2%80%94%20and%20immediately%20deposit%20it%20more%20times%20than%20I%20care%20to%20count.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUntil%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20I%20didn't%20consider%20myself%20financially%20responsible.%20I%20decided%20that%20enough%20was%20enough%2C%20and%20I%20%3Cem%3Ehad%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20get%20my%20financial%20affairs%20in%20order%3B%20I%20had%20no%20excuse%20to%20continue%20living%20like%20a%20poor%20college%20graduate%20anymore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMixing%20money%20was%20complicating%20everything%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20hired%20and%20met%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.levelupfinancialcoaching.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJoe%20Maddux%2C%20a%20money%20coach%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20early%20February%2C%20and%20his%20biggest%20recommendation%20%E2%80%94%20keeping%20my%20%26quot%3BKorean%26quot%3B%20money%20and%20my%20%26quot%3BAmerican%26quot%3B%20money%20separate%20%E2%80%94%20has%20changed%20the%20way%20I%20view%20my%20finances%2C%20how%20I%20save%20and%20spend%2C%20and%20how%20I'm%20paying%20down%20my%20debt%20(again).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20asking%20me%20to%20be%20brutally%20honest%20about%20where%20every%20cent%20I%20spent%20was%20going%2C%20Joe%20helped%20me%20see%20where%20I%20was%20making%20some%20painful%20financial%20mistakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20hadn't%20considered%20how%20much%20of%20a%20disservice%20I%20was%20doing%20myself%20every%20time%20I%20would%20pull%20money%20from%20one%20country%20to%20the%20other.%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fwhere-to-exchange-currency%5C%22%3Ecurrency%20exchange%20rate%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20the%20South%20Korean%20won%20and%20the%20U.S.%20dollar%20has%20gotten%20worse%20over%20the%20years.%20When%20I%20first%20arrived%20in%202013%2C%20the%20math%20was%20almost%20perfect%20%E2%80%94%20%241%20was%20equal%20to%20about%201%2C040%20Korean%20won.%20In%20my%20head%2C%20I%20would%20convert%20local%20price%20tags%20to%20dollars%20and%20know%20about%20what%20I%20was%20spending.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20the%20exchange%20rate%20from%20%241%20has%20fluctuated%20between%201%2C300%20and%201%2C400%20won%2C%20usually%20around%201%2C350.%20Like%20everyone%20who%20feels%20pain%20pumping%20fuel%20into%20their%20car%20when%20it's%2030%20cents%20higher%20than%20it%20was%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20every%20time%20I%20sent%20money%20back%20to%20the%20States%2C%20I%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20hemorrhaging%20cash%2C%20losing%2030%20cents%20on%20every%20dollar%20I%20sent%20back.%20And%20regardless%20of%20how%20I%20decided%20to%20move%20money%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20I%20was%20always%20losing%20some%20small%20percentage%20purely%20on%20varying%20exchange%20rates%20and%20the%20banks%20keeping%20what%20they%20considered%20their%20share.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20Joe%20helped%20me%20see%20how%20I%20was%20allowing%20my%20mindset%20of%20having%20two%20streams%20of%20income%20halfway%20across%20the%20world%20to%20justify%20making%20and%20sticking%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-budgeting-apps%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20sometimes%20living%20above%20my%20means.%20Every%20time%20I%20moved%20that%20cash%20back%20and%20forth%20instead%20of%20keeping%20it%20separated%20with%20specific%20%26quot%3Bjobs%26quot%3B%20or%20purposes%2C%20I%20was%20giving%20myself%20permission%20to%20make%20bad%20money%20decisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENeed%20help%20with%20money%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinding%20a%20financial%20advisor%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20hard.%20SmartAsset's%20free%20tool%20matches%20you%20with%20up%20to%20three%20fiduciary%20financial%20advisors%20who%20serve%20your%20area%20in%20minutes.%20Each%20advisor%20has%20been%20vetted%20by%20SmartAsset%20and%20is%20held%20to%20a%20fiduciary%20standard%20to%20act%20in%20your%20best%20interests.%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsmartasset.com%2Fretirement%2Ffind-a-financial-planner%3Futm_source%3Dbusinessinsider%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_campaign%3Dbus__falc_bicontent%26utm_content%3DBI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Start%20your%20search%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%3E'American'%20money%20stays%20in%20America%3B%20'Korean'%20money%20stays%20(mostly)%20in%20Korea%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20and%20I%20worked%20out%20a%20budget%20for%20what%20I%20could%20spend%20in%20Korea%20each%20week%20and%20month.%20I%20now%20have%20a%20%26quot%3BFinancial%20Friday%26quot%3B%20where%20I%20look%20at%20what%20I've%20spent%20over%20the%20week%20on%20my%20Korean%20credit%20card%20and%20pay%20off%20the%20balance%20for%20the%20week.%20If%20I've%20gone%20%26quot%3Bover%26quot%3B%20my%20allowance%2C%20I%20have%20to%20cut%20that%20out%20of%20the%20following%20week's%20budget.%20Weirdly%2C%20I%20%3Cem%3Elove%3C%2Fem%3E%20my%20Financial%20Fridays%20because%20it%20helps%20me%20keep%20myself%20accountable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJoe%20also%20introduced%20me%20to%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20sinking%20fund%20%E2%80%94%20the%20practice%20of%20averaging%20your%20annual%20costs%20for%20things%20and%20saving%20ahead%20of%20schedule%20for%20them.%20This%20blew%20my%20mind%20and%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20my%20life%2C%20has%20made%20saving%20%3Cem%3Efun%3C%2Fem%3E%20because%20I%20know%20I%20get%20to%20use%20it%20on%20things%20I%20enjoy%2C%20like%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20have%20%26quot%3BKorean%26quot%3B%20money%20left%20over%2C%20I%20can%20send%20it%20back%20to%20my%20U.S.%20accounts%20to%20pay%20down%20my%20accumulated%20credit%20card%20debt%20or%20keep%20it%20in%20Korea%20for%20a%20rainy%20day.%20So%20far%2C%20it's%20fallen%20into%20the%20latter%20category.%20(I%20can%20%3Cem%3Ealways%3C%2Fem%3E%20find%20a%20way%20to%20spend%20money!)%20But%20thanks%20to%20Joe's%20help%2C%20intentionally%20keeping%20my%20money%20separate%20has%20helped%20me%20take%20control%20of%20my%20financial%20life%20and%20get%20me%20closer%20to%20true%20financial%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-coach-get-more-out-money-living-abroad-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725706682000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66da14cda0ff598b26650895%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-coach-get-more-out-money-living-abroad-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20Korea%2C%20the%20exchange%20rate%20was%20easy%20to%20calculate%20in%20my%20head%2C%20but%20that%20mental%20math%20meant%20that%20I%20started%20to%20overspend.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Krissi%20Driver)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-coach-get-more-out-money-living-abroad-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20haggled%20down%20the%20price%20of%20everything%20from%20rent%20to%20dental%20surgery%2C%20and%20I%20have%206%20tips%20for%20anyone%20who%20wants%20a%20better%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20offers%20and%20details%20on%20this%20page%20may%20have%20updated%20or%20changed%20since%20the%20time%20of%20publication.%20See%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhaggling-negotiate-better-price-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20current%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAffiliate%20links%20for%20the%20products%20on%20this%20page%20are%20from%20partners%20that%20compensate%20us%20and%20terms%20apply%20to%20offers%20listed%20(see%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvertiser%20disclosure%20with%20our%20list%20of%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20more%20details).%20However%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20See%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20rate%20products%20and%20services%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20help%20you%20make%20smart%20decisions%20with%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222769%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peter%20Rothbart%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6227c60fdcce010019a748be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221384%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%2C%20Peter%20Rothbart.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Rothbart%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHaggling%20isn't%20appropriate%20in%20all%20circumstances%2C%20but%20it%20can%20bear%20fruit%20even%20when%20prices%20seem%20fixed.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThere%20is%20an%20art%20to%20haggling%2C%20and%20it%20takes%20time%20to%20learn%20how%20to%20do%20it%20effectively.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBeing%20knowledgeable%2C%20friendly%2C%20firm%2C%20%3Cstrong%3Edecisive%2C%20frugal%2C%20and%20reasonably%20flexible%20help%20when%20bargaining.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20I%20finished%20college%20in%202003%2C%20I've%20had%20a%20side%20gig%20buying%20and%20selling%20merchandise%20both%20locally%20and%20online.%20I've%20flipped%20thousands%20of%20items%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20my%20extensive%20experience%20trading%20both%20online%20and%20in%20person%20has%20taught%20me%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20strategy%20and%20etiquette%20of%20price%20negotiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20six%20lessons%20I've%20learned%20that%20can%20help%20you%20score%20a%20great%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Be%20friendly%2C%20but%20firm%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDO%20play%20nice.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Hollywood%20glorifies%20sales%20and%20marketing%20as%20the%20domain%20of%20smooth-talking%2C%20cutthroat%20hustlers%20bent%20on%20stealing%20your%20shirt%20%E2%80%94%20but%20while%20high-pressure%20bargaining%20tactics%20may%20seem%20charismatic%20or%20charming%20on%20the%20big%20screen%2C%20they%20don't%20translate%20to%20everyday%20life.%20You'll%20be%20better%20served%20by%20good%20manners%20and%20a%20few%20kind%20words.%20Be%20polite%2C%20stay%20positive%2C%20and%20remember%3A%20The%20more%20pleasant%20you%20are%20to%20work%20with%2C%20the%20more%20deals%20you'll%20get%20done.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EDON'T%20be%20a%20pushover.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Being%20polite%20doesn't%20mean%20being%20overly%20accommodating%2C%20however.%20You%20don't%20owe%20it%20to%20anyone%20to%20accept%20a%20bad%20deal%20for%20courtesy's%20sake.%20Set%20your%20terms%20and%20stick%20to%20them.%20If%20you%20can't%20reach%20an%20agreement%2C%20then%20so%20be%20it.%20Failing%20to%20close%20a%20deal%20is%20not%20a%20breach%20of%20etiquette%2C%20so%20you%20shouldn't%20take%20it%20personally%20if%20you%20and%20the%20other%20party%20don't%20see%20eye%20to%20eye.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Be%20perceptive%2C%20not%20presumptuous%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDO%20be%20mindful%20of%20context.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAttitudes%20about%20haggling%20vary%20culturally%2C%20regionally%2C%20personally%2C%20and%20situationally.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20find%20folks%20in%20Seattle%20less%20comfortable%20with%20price%20negotiations%20than%20the%20Michiganders%20I%20grew%20up%20with%2C%20and%20I%20generally%20get%20more%20traction%20naming%20my%20price%20at%20a%20local%20swap%20meet%20than%20at%20the%20mall.%20Pay%20attention%20to%20how%20your%20haggling%20attempts%20are%20received.%20If%20someone%20seems%20reluctant%20to%20negotiate%2C%20respect%20their%20stance%20and%20carry%20on.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EDON'T%20make%20assumptions.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Haggling%20may%20work%20even%20in%20circumstances%20that%20are%20typically%20non-negotiable.%20For%20example%2C%20I've%20haggled%20over%20the%20cost%20of%20retail%20goods%20at%20big-box%20stores%2C%20monthly%20rental%20payments%2C%20compensation%20for%20a%20delayed%20or%20oversold%20flight%2C%20and%20even%20dental%20surgery%20during%20a%20time%20when%20I%20didn't%20have%20insurance.%20Use%20your%20judgment%20to%20decide%20where%20you%20feel%20haggling%20is%20or%20isn't%20appropriate%2C%20but%20to%20quote%20hockey%20legend%20Wayne%20Gretzky%3A%20You%20miss%20100%25%20of%20the%20shots%20you%20don't%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Know%20more%2C%20pay%20less%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDO%20research%20the%20market.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Seek%20out%20comparable%20items%20for%20sale%20to%20establish%20a%20baseline%20price%20and%20assess%20your%20options.%20You'll%20have%20more%20leverage%20if%20you%20can%20get%20a%20similar%20deal%20elsewhere%2C%20and%20less%20if%20the%20deal%20in%20front%20of%20you%20is%20unique.%20Either%20way%2C%20use%20that%20knowledge%20to%20hone%20your%20offer%20and%2C%20when%20possible%2C%20look%20at%20selling%20prices%20rather%20than%20listing%20prices%20to%20get%20a%20clearer%20sense%20of%20fair%20market%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDON'T%20mistake%20similar%20for%20equivalent.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Look%20for%20differences%20between%20available%20items%20and%20the%20one%20you're%20eyeing%2C%20like%20the%20model%20number%20and%20specifications%2C%20subtle%20wear%20that%20might%20diminish%20the%20value%2C%20or%20accessories%20that%20might%20augment%20it.%20Account%20for%20costs%20like%20taxes%20and%20shipping%2C%20and%20consider%20external%20factors%20like%20time%2C%20distance%2C%20and%20convenience.%20If%20you%20have%20to%20drive%20an%20extra%20hour%20to%20save%20%2410%2C%20that's%20not%20really%20a%20better%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Be%20frugal%2C%20not%20cheap%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDO%20bid%20to%20your%20advantage.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Start%20by%20offering%20less%20than%20you're%20ultimately%20willing%20to%20pay%20%E2%80%94%20or%20as%20a%20seller%2C%20list%20items%20for%20sale%20above%20the%20minimum%20you'll%20accept.%20Your%20first%20offer%20may%20be%20accepted%2C%20but%20if%20not%2C%20you'll%20still%20have%20room%20to%20negotiate%20below%20your%20ceiling.%20Conventional%20wisdom%20says%20naming%20a%20price%20first%20puts%20you%20at%20a%20disadvantage%2C%20but%20that's%20only%20a%20concern%20for%20high-stakes%20negotiations%3B%20I%20wouldn't%20sweat%20it%20when%20you're%20buying%20a%20coffee%20table%20off%20Craigslist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20price%20isn't%20the%20only%20variable%20in%20play.%20All%20aspects%20of%20a%20transaction%20are%20open%20to%20negotiation.%20If%20you're%20in%20a%20position%20to%20offer%20other%20favorable%20terms%20%E2%80%94%20like%20your%20own%20muscle%20or%20vehicle%20to%20move%20a%20heavy%20piece%20of%20furniture%20%E2%80%94%20make%20that%20clear%20from%20the%20start%20to%20help%20your%20offer%20stand%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDON'T%20blow%20a%20good%20deal%20looking%20for%20a%20better%20one.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20you're%20presented%20with%20a%20strong%20offer%2C%20take%20it.%20Trying%20to%20chip%20away%20at%20a%20favorable%20deal%20leaves%20the%20door%20open%20for%20someone%20else%20to%20swoop%20in%2C%20and%20make%20your%20opportunity%20their%20own.%20Best%20to%20complete%20the%20transaction%20and%20let%20good%20enough%20be%20good%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDON'T%20give%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3Elowball%20offers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20with%20little%20chance%20of%20success.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20That%20tells%20the%20seller%20you're%20not%20serious%20and%20starts%20off%20negotiations%20inhospitably.%20Before%20you%20name%20a%20price%2C%20consider%20whether%20you%20would%20accept%20the%20same%20amount%20if%20the%20roles%20were%20reversed.%20If%20the%20answer%20is%20a%20resounding%20no%2C%20then%20your%20offer%20probably%20isn't%20reasonable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Act%20decisively%2C%20not%20hastily%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDO%20strike%20while%20the%20iron%20is%20hot.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Nothing%20pleases%20me%20more%20as%20a%20seller%20than%20a%20buyer%20who%20offers%20to%20pay%20cash%20and%20close%20a%20deal%20quickly.%20I'll%20happily%20lower%20my%20asking%20price%20if%20it%20means%20moving%20an%20item%20now%20rather%20than%20the%20possibility%20of%20getting%20top%20dollar%20later.%20Cash%20talks%2C%20and%20expedience%20is%20an%20asset%2C%20so%20employ%20both%20when%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDON'T%20rush.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20While%20you%20%3Cem%3Eshould%3C%2Fem%3E%20act%20quickly%20to%20secure%20a%20true%20bargain%2C%20you%20shouldn't%20feel%20compelled%20to%20act%20when%20you're%20uncertain.%20Silence%20your%20FOMO%20and%20ignore%20any%20pressure%20tactics%20applied%20by%20the%20other%20party.%20Trust%20your%20gut%2C%20and%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20your%20own%20inner%20peace%2C%20try%20not%20to%20doubt%20yourself%20once%20you've%20made%20a%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Set%20limits%2C%20not%20limitations%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDO%20have%20a%20plan.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Figuring%20out%20what%20you're%20willing%20to%20pay%20ahead%20of%20time%20will%20help%20you%20stay%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fhow-to-budget%5C%22%3Ebudget%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20frames%20the%20negotiation%20so%20you%20can%20bid%20strategically.%20When%20you've%20exhausted%20options%20and%20can't%20reach%20a%20satisfactory%20deal%2C%20a%20take-it-or-leave-it%20offer%20at%20your%20limit%20is%20an%20effective%20final%20bargaining%20strategy%2C%20since%20it%20puts%20the%20decision%20on%20the%20other%20party.%20If%20that%20fails%2C%20be%20willing%20to%20walk%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDON'T%20be%20a%20robot.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Price%20negotiation%20is%20a%20dynamic%20process%2C%20and%20you'll