22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebirthed%20three%20kids%20in%20three%20years%20in%20New%20York%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20California%2C%20the%20last%20emotion%20I%20expected%20was%20loneliness.%20I%20was%20with%20the%20man%20I%20adored.%20We%20were%20surrounded%20by%20new%20life%20that%20had%20come%20from%20our%20love.%20One%20sister%20lived%20nearby%2C%20and%20we%20had%20many%20friends.%20So%20why%20did%20I%20feel%20like%20our%20house%20was%20an%20island%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-parents-set-their-kids-up-for-success-2016-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EParenting%20books%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20social%20media%20photos%20at%20birthdays%2C%20dinners%2C%20playdates%2C%20and%20family%20gatherings%20made%20everybody%20appear%20overjoyed%20and%20connected%2C%20but%20they%20also%20made%20me%20feel%20completely%20distant%20from%20my%20experience.%20Our%20family%20was%20nothing%20like%20those%20images.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-congenital-heart-disease%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ea%20baby%20with%20a%20heart%20condition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20one%20who%20contracted%20a%20rare%20disease%20from%20a%20tick%20bite%2C%20and%20a%20third%20who%20contracted%20pneumonia%2C%20all%20needing%20patience%2C%20love%2C%20and%20strength%20as%20they%20were%20born%20one%20after%20the%20other.%20As%20we%20grew%2C%20what%20defined%20our%20marriage%20and%20parenting%20experience%20was%20its%20lack%20of%20predictability%20and%20its%20mystery.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I'll%20be%20honest.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-little-kids-can-be-exhausting-and-stressful-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERaising%20kids%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20made%20dating%2C%20maintaining%20friendships%2C%20and%20socializing%20anything%20but%20easy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20had%20to%20take%20immediate%20measures%20to%20stay%20connected%20to%20that%20world%2C%20to%20stay%20vibrant%20as%20a%20couple.%20So%20my%20partner's%20mom%20stayed%20with%20our%20baby%20while%20we%20left%20the%20hospital%20for%20a%20date%20or%20two.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20seemed%20crazy%2C%20but%20we%20did%20it.%20It%20turns%20out%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstopping-date-night-saved-my-marriage-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethe%20habit%20of%20dating%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20especially%20during%20crises%2C%20would%20become%20the%20anchor%20of%20our%20relationship.%20Since%20then%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20tough%20things%20become%2C%20we%20honor%20our%20weekly%20date%20nights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f68c2435-4dee-44d3-b798-d0607620f258%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20tried%20different%20things%20together%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20attended%20different%20churches%20as%20a%20family.%20At%20church%2C%20we%20were%20given%20childcare%2C%20at%20least%20an%20hour%20to%20sit%2C%20and%20a%20chance%20to%20contemplate.%20Singing%2C%20praying%2C%20and%20listening%20engaged%20our%20hearts%20in%20worlds%20beyond%20practicality%20and%20parenting%20together.%20Recently%2C%20we%20stopped%20attending%20church%2C%20finding%20God%20in%20a%20broader%20sphere.%20Still%20we're%20forever%20grateful%20for%20the%20way%20our%20hearts%20were%20held%20at%20church%20by%20strangers%20and%20friends%20in%20our%20toughest%20times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20also%20volunteered%20together.%20Hosting%20refugee%20families%20for%20dinners%2C%20weekend%20stays%2C%20outings%20to%20the%20beach%2C%20sports%20activities%2C%20and%20other%20events%20revealed%20how%20families%20from%20unimaginable%20crises%20still%20maintain%20love%20and%20still%20survive.%20These%20friendships%20became%20most%20valuable%20to%20me.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226b5f3844-c984-4d27-9667-a7fa01c9709a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20decided%20to%20move%20abroad%20and%20travel%20more%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20we%20had%20to%20work%20to%20leave%20the%20house.%20Then%2C%20we%20left%20the%20continent%2C%20moving%20our%20family%20to%20Switzerland%20in%20search%20of%20new%2C%20meaningful%20connections.%20This%20lifestyle%20change%20brought%20us%20closer%2C%20as%20the%20international%20community%20of%20parents%20welcomed%20us%20in%20a%20more%20open%20way%20than%20I'd%20felt%20in%20my%20life.%20Moving%20overseas%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20decisions%20we%20made%20for%20our%20relationship%20and%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20cycled%20regularly%20all%20over%20Europe%2C%20sometimes%20with%20friends%20but%20also%20simply%20enjoying%20and%20challenging%20each%20other.%20Along%20the%20way%2C%20we%20met%20unusual%20people%2C%20like%20a%20vineyard%20owner%20who%20told%20us%20his%20life%20story%20while%20feeding%20us%20wine%20and%20almonds.%20We%20burned%20calories%2C%20sweated%2C%20ate%2C%20and%20drank%2C%20and%20shared%20our%20journeys%20with%20cycling%20friends%20worldwide.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20lived%20in%20New%20York%2C%20Connecticut%2C%20and%20San%20Francisco%2C%20and%20our%20kids%20were%20little%2C%20we%20tried%20not%20to%20stay%20on%20our%20block.%20Travel%20could%20mean%20simply%20visiting%20a%20new%20park%2C%20beach%2C%20or%20neighborhood%20where%20we'd%20be%20forced%20to%20interact%20with%20new%20parents%20and%20observe%20life%20unlike%20our%20everyday%20world.%20When%20we%20moved%20to%20Europe%20and%20our%20kids%20grew%2C%20we%20broadened%20our%20travels%20into%20mountains%2C%20other%20countries%2C%20lakes%2C%20and%20seas%2C%20where%20our%20social%20opportunities%20expanded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220dc5720a-3f1b-4c7d