3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20transported%20to%20some%20kind%20of%20utopia%2C%20unlike%20anything%20I%20had%20ever%20been%20to%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Hudgens%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vogue.com%2Fslideshow%2Fvanessa-hudgens-and-cole-tucker-wedding%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVogue%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20her%20December%202023%20wedding.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20whimsical%20and%20magical%2C%20and%20I%20just%20fell%20in%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20my%20first%20two%20trips%20to%20Tulum%2C%20I%20drove%20by%20Azulik%20a%20number%20of%20times%20and%20was%20extremely%20intrigued%20by%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20candlelit%20luxury%20treehouse.%20So%20when%20I%20headed%20back%20in%20May%20to%20check%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftulum-airport-review-location-airlines-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebrand-new%20Tulum%20airport%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20knew%20exactly%20where%20I%20would%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20I%20left%20for%20Tulum%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20Azulik's%20origins.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Walkway%20at%20Azulik%20resort%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669e89cc80d4d5da13d5e692%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETulum's%20resort%20is%20connected%20via%20these%20unique%20suspended%20pathways%2C%20made%20of%20branches.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAzulik%20was%20dreamed%20up%20and%20designed%20by%20the%20architect%20Eduardo%20%26quot%3BRoth%26quot%3B%20Neira%2C%20who%20was%20hailed%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fabinlot%2F2019%2F09%2F23%2Fmeet-roth-the-hotelier-seeking-to-save-tulum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EForbes%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%20as%20%26quot%3Bthe%20hotelier%20seeking%20to%20save%20Tulum.%26quot%3B%20Dismayed%20with%20how%20Tulum's%20landscape%20had%20been%20razed%20to%20build%20hotels%20for%20the%20growing%20influx%20of%20tourists%2C%20Roth%20set%20out%20to%20create%20a%20resort%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Breconnect%20people%20with%20the%20natural%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20destroying%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Forbes.%20%26quot%3BSo%20what%20I%20tried%20to%20do%20is%20respect%20nature%2C%20and%20not%20cut%20any%20trees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAzulik's%20restaurants%20and%20villas%20are%20connected%20via%20pathways%20made%20of%20linked%20logs%20suspended%20over%20the%20ground%2C%20meant%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20space%20for%20the%20animals%20to%20crawl%20below%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20resort's%20website%20states.%20Their%20windy%20trails%2C%20which%20twist%20and%20turn%20around%20the%20jungle%2C%20are%20an%20intentional%20rejection%20of%20straight%20lines%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3Ba%20human%20invention.%26quot%3B%20Lush%20trees%20and%20fauna%20provide%20a%20protective%20canopy%20around%20the%20resort%2C%20allowed%20to%20%26quot%3Bcontinue%20their%20journey%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20jungle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECall%20me%20a%20hopeless%20romantic%20or%20an%20easy%20target%2C%20but%20it%20all%20sounded%20poetic.%20Would%20the%20experience%20live%20up%20to%20its%20admirable%20origins%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20stay%20began%20in%20the%20check-in%20lounge%2C%20where%20I%20was%20immediately%20handed%20a%20clipboard%20with%20a%20two-page%20disclaimer.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azulik%20check-in%20lounge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669e89b72d66759f66fcf526%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lobby%20at%20Azulik.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20our%20stay%20with%20paperwork%20didn't%20exactly%20scream%20%3Cem%3Eluxury%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20was%20quite%20different%20from%20the%20peaceful%20check-in%20process%20I%20had%20experienced%20two%20days%20earlier%20at%20La%20Valise%2C%20where%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20had%20been%20greeted%20with%20fresh%20margaritas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20we%20dutifully%20carried%20our%20clipboards%20to%20a%20couch%2C%20where%20I%20began%20reading%20the%20disclaimer.%20It%20first%20noted%20that%20we%20were%20%26quot%3Bassuming%20the%20risk%20of%20staying%20in%20a%20place%20surrounded%20by%20the%20lushness%20of%20the%20jungle%26quot%3B%20and%20advised%20that%20we%20do%20not%20come%20into%20contact%20with%20or%20feed%20the%20animals.%20Fair%20enough!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20were%20the%20fees%3A%20%2420%20in%20case%20we%20lost%20the%20%26quot%3Baccess%20control%20wristband%26quot%3B%20(a%20piece%20of%20string)%2C%20%2420%20if%20we%20lost%20the%20magnetic%20key%2C%20and%20%24200%20for%20smoking.%20But%20most%20surprising%20was%20the%20note%20that%20it%20was%20strictly%20forbidden%20to%20use%20a%20professional%20camera%20within%20the%20hotel%2C%20the%20noncompliance%20of%20which%20could%20result%20in%20a%20charge%20of%20%2415%2C000.%20By%20signing%20the%20disclosure%2C%20I%20authorized%20the%20resort%20to%20use%20my%20credit%20card%20on%20file%20for%20%26quot%3Bthe%20full%20payment%20of%20all%20charges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20no%20professional%20camera%2C%20I%20balked%20at%20the%20over-the-top%20fee.%20Welcome%20to%20Azulik.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20our%20disclaimers%20were%20signed%2C%20it%20was%20time%20for%20a%20tour.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azulik%20Resort%20in%20Tulum%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d7fb22d66759f66fcc2ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaterways%20glisten%20under%20the%20suspended%20pathways%20throughout%20the%20resort.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20in%20a%20flowing%20Grecian%20dress%20introduced%20herself%20as%20one%20of%20Azulik's%20%26quot%3Bangels%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20term%20they%20use%20for%20their%20staff%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20we%20left%20the%20dark%20lounge%20and%20walked%20out%20into%20the%20lush%20jungle%2C%20I%20was%20briefly%20struck%20by%20the%20resort's%20beauty.%20The%20waterways%20throughout%20the%20hotel%20glistened%20under%20the%20sun%2C%20and%20the%20flourishing%20trees%20provided%20gorgeous%20scenery%20and%20comforting%20shade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20we%20began%20to%20walk%20around%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20the%20pathways%20were%20quite%20%E2%80%A6%20bumpy.%20The%20curvy%20branches%20were%20of%20different%20sizes%20and%20lengths%2C%20creating%20an%20irregular%20floor.%20On%20its%20website%2C%20Azulik%20says%20this%20%26quot%3Binvites%20us%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20our%20every%20step.%26quot%3B%20It%20also%20notes%20that%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20children%20aren't%20permitted%20on%20the%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20was%20fine%20to%20walk%20the%20pathways%2C%20my%20mom%2C%C2%A0who%20is%20in%20her%2060s%2C%20struggled%20a%20bit.%20The%20website%20notes%20that%20the%20Azulik%20rooms%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20suitable%20for%20people%20with%20disabilities%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20the%20pathways%20could%20be%20tough%20even%20if%20you%20just%20have%20issues%20with%20your%20back%20or%20knees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20we%20walked%20through%20one%20of%20the%20lounges%2C%20I%20stopped%20to%20check%20out%20the%20event%20schedule%20written%20on%20a%20chalkboard.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azulik%20activity%20board%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d7fcbfb2b6bedb0590d88%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20activity%20board%20in%20an%20Azulik%20lounge%20showcased%20a%20range%20of%20classes%20and%20workshops.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAzulik%20has%20a%20range%20of%20activities%20for%20its%20guests%2C%20including%20daily%20vinyasa%20yoga%20at%208%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkshops%20on%20ego%20masks%2C%20flower%20mandalas%2C%20and%20%26quot%3Bhealing%20the%20inner%20child%26quot%3B%20are%20also%20offered%20throughout%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThen%2C%20it%20was%20time%20for%20Azulik's%20traditional%20%26quot%3Benergy%20cleansing%26quot%3B%20welcome%20ceremony.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azulik%20greeting%20ritual%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d7fe3fb2b6bedb0590d8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20had%20our%20welcome%20ceremony%20in%20this%20tent%2C%20standing%20on%20the%20wooden%20platform.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mother%20and%20I%20dutifully%20waited%20as%20three%20friends%20handed%20their%20phones%20to%20one%20of%20the%20angels%20to%20take%20a%20video%20of%20them%20as%20the%20ceremony%20began.%20They%20stepped%20onto%20a%20wooden%20platform%2C%20grasped%20each%20other's%20hands%2C%20and%20shut%20their%20eyes%20as%20a%20woman%20wafted%20incense%20around%20them.%20We%20learned%20that%20this%20ceremony%20was%20meant%20to%20help%20guide%20us%20into%20a%20state%20of%20deep%20relaxation%20and%20leave%20the%20negative%20energies%20and%20stress%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIs%20this%20just%20an%20Instagram%20gimmick%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20tried%20to%20push%20down%20the%20cynical%20thought%20as%20my%20mother%20and%20I%20stepped%20onto%20the%20platform%20and%20grabbed%20each%20other's%20hands%20when%20it%20was%20our%20turn.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%2C%20reminding%20myself%20that%20this%20was%20all%20part%20of%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOnce%20the