2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fazulik-hotel-tulum-villa-room-eco-resort-photos-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYou%20can%20find%20my%20full%20room%20tour%20at%20Azulik%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESince%20the%20villa%20has%20no%20electric%20lights%2C%20there%20were%20candles%20spread%20throughout%20the%20space.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azulik%20resort%20candles%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66c8b45743b5e59d16b4b673%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20staff%20member%20comes%20into%20each%20room%20to%20light%20the%20tea%20candles%20every%20night%20when%20the%20sun%20sets.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20every%20Azulik%20villa%20has%20WiFi%20and%20a%20power%20outlet%20to%20charge%20your%20phone%2C%20there%20are%20no%20lamps.%20Instead%2C%20a%20staff%20member%20comes%20by%20every%20night%20to%20light%20all%20the%20tea%20candles%20as%20the%20sun%20goes%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20its%20website%2C%20this%20is%20an%20intentional%20choice%20that%20Azulik%20hopes%20will%20%26quot%3Bcreate%20an%20atmosphere%20of%20tranquility.%26quot%3B%20The%20resort%20also%20notes%20that%20it%20wanted%20to%20forego%20any%20%26quot%3Blight%20pollution%20that%20severely%20impacts%20the%20environment%20of%20creatures%20like%20sea%20turtles.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20were%20also%20surprised%20to%20find%20that%20there%20was%20no%20shower.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azulik%20treehouse%20tub%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d8050fb2b6bedb0590d98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20room's%20handmade%20mosaic%20bathtub.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20villa%20at%20Azulik%20comes%20with%20a%20handmade%20mosaic%20bathtub.%20Its%20website%20says%20this%20is%20meant%20to%20encourage%20guests%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20your%20time%2C%20soak%20in%20the%20tub%20with%20bath%20salts%2C%20and%20relax.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beautiful%20mosaic%20bathtub%2C%20decorated%20with%20hand-painted%20blue%20flowers%2C%20matched%20the%20nearby%20sink.%20Half%20a%20coconut%20shell%20rested%20on%20the%20edge%20to%20help%20with%20bathing.%20The%20usual%20provided%20toiletries%20were%20available%2C%20but%20alas%2C%20no%20bath%20salts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAs%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20walked%20around%20the%20resort%2C%20we%20realized%20much%20of%20the%20space%20was%20dedicated%20to%20the%20spa.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Azulik%20massage%20pool%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d81452d66759f66fcc322%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20of%20the%20spa's%20many%20pools%20and%20massage%20beds.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20saw%20several%20pools%2C%20like%20the%20one%20above%2C%20which%20featured%20two%20massage%20beds%20set%20up%20for%20upcoming%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20beds%20overlooked%20the%20ocean%2C%20allowing%20guests%20to%20enjoy%20the%20sound%20of%20crashing%20waves%20during%20their%20services.%20It%20was%20a%20stunning%20setup%20that%20matched%20the%20unique%20design%20of%20the%20spa%2C%20which%20I%20got%20a%20full%20view%20of%20the%20following%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20found%20it%20a%20bit%20strange%20that%20there%20were%20so%20many%20miniature%20pools%20dedicated%20to%20decoration%20when%20Azulik%20didn't%20have%20an%20actual%20pool%20for%20guests%20to%20swim%20in.%20Tulum's%20beaches%20are%20frequently%20covered%20in%20sargassum%20during%20its%20seaweed%20season%20(around%20May%20to%20October)%2C%20so%20no%20pool%20seemed%20like%20a%20strange%20choice%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20a%20luxury%20resort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20then%20headed%20to%20the%20rooftop%20for%20Azulik's%20famed%20sunset%20hour.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Anneta%20at%20Azulik%20during%20sunset%20hour%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d924f51d8d2deb96b913ed%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20rooftop%20had%20suspended%20nets%2C%20allowing%20you%20to%20sit%20over%20the%20resort.%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAzulik's%20daily%20sunset%20hour%20begins%20at%205%20p.m.%2C%20and%20there%20are%20no%20reservations%20%E2%80%94%20spots%20are%20given%20on%20a%20first-come%2C%20first-served%20basis.%20The%20experience%20is%20free%20for%20guests%20and%20%2450%20for%20the%20general%20public%2C%20which%20includes%20a%20complimentary%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20making%20our%20way%20up%20several%20staircases%2C%20we%20were%20met%20with%20the%20sounds%20of%20melodic%20techno.%20%26quot%3BThis%20feels%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fburning-man-experience-biggest-misconceptions-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurning%20Man%3C%2Fa%3E%20light%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20wrote%20in%20my%20notes%20as%20I%20spotted%20the%20moody%20DJ%20with%20a%20leopard-print%20pashmina%20slung%20over%20his%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20a%20popular%20event%2C%20only%20a%20few%20small%20tables%20were%20set%20up%20on%20the%20expansive%20roof.%20Most%20people%20stood%20and%20held%20their%20drinks%2C%20while%20some%20opted%20to%20lie%20down%20on%20the%20suspended%20nets%20over%20the%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMost%20of%20the%20seating%20was%20reserved%20for%20the%20private%20VIP%20%26quot%3Bnests.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D