%20at%20Azulik%20is%20beautifully%20designed.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20open-air%20spa%20was%20breathtaking%2C%20full%20of%20lush%20trees%20and%20glistening%20waterways.%20The%20extensive%20menu%20included%20the%20typical%20massages%20and%20facials%2C%20as%20well%20as%20temazcal%20and%20cacao%20ceremonies%2C%20sound%20healing%2C%20tarot%20and%20solar%20return%20readings%2C%20meditation%20classes%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20strolling%20past%20all%20the%20massage%20beds%20the%20day%20before%2C%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20couldn't%20resist%20booking%20a%20service.%20Our%20massage%20beds%20were%20set%20up%20by%20one%20of%20the%20cliffs%20overlooking%20the%20sea%2C%20and%20the%20experience%20was%20downright%20heavenly.%20It's%20been%20months%20since%20our%20trip%2C%20and%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20still%20reminisce%20about%20those%20massages.%20They%20were%20among%20the%20best%20we've%20ever%20had.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20also%20cheaper%20than%20I%20expected%2C%20costing%206%2C600%20pesos%2C%20or%20around%20%24330%2C%20for%20both%20services.%20Since%20the%20spa%20is%20open%20to%20non-guests%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20visiting%20it%20if%20you%20want%20some%20pampering%20on%20your%20next%20Tulum%20vacation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBefore%20checking%20out%20of%20the%20resort%2C%20we%20stopped%20by%20Kin%20Toh%20for%20lunch.%20Unfortunately%2C%20the%20food%20was%20just%20as%20disappointing%20as%20Tseen%20Ja.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tacos%20from%20Kin%20Toh%20restaurant%20at%20Azulik%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d838e2d66759f66fcc3ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20plate%20of%20tacos%20at%20Kin%20Toh.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20Tseen%20Ja%2C%20Kin%20Toh%2C%20located%20right%20under%20the%20rooftop%2C%20is%20beautifully%20designed.%20The%20restaurant's%20many%20windows%20let%20you%20spot%20the%20tops%20of%20trees.%20The%20wooden%20tables%20are%20decorated%20with%20lovely%20runners%2C%20designed%20to%20look%20like%20sand%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20beginning%20of%20lunch%20was%20promising%20as%20our%20frothy%20pi%C3%B1a%20coladas%20and%20fresh%20guacamole%20arrived%20at%20the%20table.%20Then%20the%20tacos%20came%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20tried%20four%20different%20tacos%2C%20costing%20between%20220%20to%20230%20pesos%2C%20or%20around%20%2411.%20It's%20quite%20the%20excessive%20price%20per%20taco%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20make%20up%20for%20it%20in%20flavor.%20The%20flank%20steak%20we%20tried%20was%20dry%2C%20the%20shrimp%20was%20flavorless%2C%20and%20everything%20lacked%20sauce.%20The%20only%20taco%20my%20mom%20and%20I%20kind%20of%20enjoyed%20was%20the%20chicken%2C%20which%20had%20been%20marinated%20in%20orange%20juice.%20We%20regretted%20only%20ordering%20one%2C%20but%20we%20had%20a%20plane%20to%20catch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStomachs%20still%20grumbling%2C%20our%20journey%20at%20Azulik%20had%20come%20to%20an%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAzulik%20is%20a%20stunning%20place%2C%20but%20much%20of%20our%20experience%20felt%20like%20a%20tourist%20trap%20rather%20than%20a%20luxury%20resort.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kin%20Toh%20restaurant%20at%20Azulik%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F669d835dfb2b6bedb0590e5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20entrance%20to%20Azulik's%20Kin%20Toh%20restaurant.%20%3Cp%3EAnneta%20Konstantinides%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20no%20denying%20that%20Azulik%20is%20beautifully%20designed.%20Walking%20over%20its%20waterways%20and%20climbing%20the%20stairs%20to%20its%20treehouse%20restaurants%2C%20I%20felt%20transported%20to%20a%20real%20jungle%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20food%20was%20nowhere%20near%20the%20quality%20of%20what%20a%20luxury%20resort%20should%20offer%2C%20especially%20at%20such%20exorbitant%20prices.%20The%20hidden%20fees%20and%20emphasis%20on%20VIP%20nests%20also%20felt%20like%20the%20resort%20was%20just%20trying%20to%20make%20as%20much%20money%20off%20its%20guests%20as%20possible.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spa%20was%20a%20lovely%20experience%2C%20though.%C2%A0It's%20a%20much%20better%20way%20to%20see%20the%20resort%20as%20a%20non-guest%20than%20going%20to%20sunset%20hour%20or%20eating%20at%20one%20of%20the%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20say%20a%20picture's%20worth%20a%20thousand%20words.%20But%20at%20Azulik%2C%20there's%20far%20more%20to%20the%20story%20than%20what%20you%20see%20on%20Instagram.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftulum-azulik-hotel-review-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725704282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66da0fc51d8d2deb96b99ec8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftulum-azulik-hotel-review-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Azulik%20is%20a%20luxury%20resort%20in%20Tulum%2C%20Mexico.%20Its%20treehouse%20villas%20are%20lit%20by%20candlelight%2C%20and%20its%20sunset%20hour%20has%20become%20a%20big%20tourist%20attraction.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22akonstantinides%40businessinsider.com%20(Anneta%20Konstantinides)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftulum-azulik-hotel-review-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20and%20more%20Gen%20Zers%20are%20struggling%20to%20stay%20in%20work%20or%20school.%20With%20%24350%20monthly%2C%20a%20New%20Orleans%20guaranteed%20income%20program%20hoped%20to%20change%20that.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bourbon%20St.%20in%20New%20Orleans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d095dd392a3bda9f231a68%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENew%20Orleans%20gave%20%24350%20monthly%20to%20young%20people%20disconnected%20from%20school%20and%20work.%3Cp%3EPeter%20Unger%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20Orleans'%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20pilot%20gave%20%24350%20monthly%20to%20125%20young%20people.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20pilot%20aimed%20to%20reduce%20poverty%20risk%20for%20teens%20and%20young%20adults%20disconnected%20from%20work%20and%20school.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EParticipants%20saw%20increased%20employment%2C%20but%20some%20struggled%20financially%20after%20payments%20ended.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20some%20young%20New%20Orleans%20residents%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhich-states-cities-have-guaranteed-basic-income-programs-low-income-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%3C%2Fa%3E%20helped%20them%20afford%20a%20ride%20to%20work.%20For%20others%2C%20the%20money%20helped%20cover%20school%20supplies%20and%20uniforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBetween%20April%202022%20and%20January%202023%2C%20the%20city%20gave%20125%20young%20people%20%24350%20a%20month%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-helps-parents-afford-toys-children-improves-quality-life-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eno%20strings%20attached%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20program%20intended%20to%20fill%20gaps%20in%20the%20social%20safety%20net%20(which%20includes%20programs%20like%20SNAP%2C%20Medicaid%2C%20and%20rental%20vouchers)%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20alleviate%20financial%20stress%20for%20people%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2016%20and%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20participants%20were%20considered%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-disconnected-youth-retirement-no-income-buy-home-anxiety-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopportunity%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20not%20enrolled%20in%20work%20or%20school%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pilot.%20They%20could%20spend%20their%20monthly%20%24350%20however%20they%20chose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResearchers%20released%20the%20program's%20final%20results%20on%20September%203.%20Per%20the%20report%2C%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20helped%20some%20participants%20secure%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbasic-income-parents-afford-childcare-get-stable-jobs-gbi-ubi-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efull-time%20employment%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20pursue%20educational%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20participant%2C%20whose%20name%20was%20withheld%20in%20the%20report%20for%20privacy%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etold%20researchers%20they%20used%20their%20%24350%20to%20replace%20a%20broken%20laptop%20so%20they%20could%20enroll%20in%20a%20coding%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20able%20to%20go%20get%20the%20computer%20and%20solve%20that%20problem%20with%20no%20stress%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20made%20me%20feel%20great%20%E2%80%94%20because%20if%20I%20wouldn't%20have%20had%20it%2C%20it%20would've%20been%20totally%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Orleans%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20pilot%20was%20a%20collaboration%20between%20Mayor%20LaToya%20Cantrell's%20Office%20of%20Youth%20and%20Families%20and%20the%20national%20advocacy%20network%20Mayors%20for%20a%20Guaranteed%20Income%20(MGI).%20The%20research%20was%20led%20by%20The%20Center%20for%20Guaranteed%20Income%20Research%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%2C%20and%20the%20cash%20payments%20were%20largely%20financed%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnola.gov%2Fnext%2Fmayors-office%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fmay-2022%2Fcity-of-new-orleans-announces-launch-of-guaranteed-income-program%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24500%2C000%20MGI%20grant%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20100%20similar%20guaranteed%20basic%20income%20programs%20have%20been%20launched%20across%20America%2C%20offering%20participants%20recurring%20cash%20payments%20for%20a%20set%20period%20of%20time.%20The%20cash%20payment%20model%20has%20been%20tried%20in%20cities%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flos-angeles-guaranteed-basic-income-pilot-ubi-partner-violence-employment-2024-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DLos%2520Angeles%2520gave%2520families%2520%25241%252C000%2CNow%2520the%2520results%2520are%2520in.%26amp%3Btext%3DThe%2520largest%2520basic%2520income%2520pilot%2Csecurity%252C%2520and%2520safer%2520home%2520situations.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELos%20Angeles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Birmingham%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchicago-basic-income-helped-mother-rent-an-apartment-ubi-gbi2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChicago%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Denver%20to%20combat%20local%20poverty%20and%20increase%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-emergency-cash-rent-homes-government-housing-aid-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccess%20to%20food%20and%20housing%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMuch%20of%20New%20Orleans'%20recent%20GBI%20efforts%20have%20been%20on%20young%20people.%20Alongside%20guaranteed%20income%20for%20opportunity%20youth%2C%20the%20nonprofit%20Rooted%20School%20Foundation%20has%20been%20giving%20local%20high%20school%20students%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rootedschool.org%2Fthe-50-dollar-study-a-youth-cash-transfer-program%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%2450%20a%20week%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20New%20Orleans%20participants%20said%20their%20benefits%20from%20guaranteed%20income%20were%20temporary.%20After%20the%20pilot%20ended%2C%20some%20young%20people%20said%20they%20still%20struggled%20to%20afford%20groceries%20and%20pay%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228ceeeab1-e7ca-4fc4-bf31-a29a248d5371%5C%22%3EGuaranteed%20income%20helps%20opportunity%20youth%20secure%20jobs%2C%20pay%20for%20housing%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20one%20in%20six%20young%20people%20in%20Louisiana%20are%20not%20working%20or%20in%20school%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Black%20youth%20make%20up%20about%20half%20of%20the%20state's%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-increasingly-no-income-cannot-retire-or-buy-houses-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopportunity%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20population%20%E2%80%94%20according%20to%20the%20New%20Orleans%20report.%20Additionally%2C%20lower%20educational%20attainment%20and%20work%20experience%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisconnected-youth-a-tale-of-2-gen-zs-in-america-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisk%20factors%20for%20future%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20New%20Orleans%20GBI%20results%20are%20based%20on%20interviews%20and%20surveys%20with%20participants%20about%20their%20experience%2C%20as%20well%20as%20quantitative%20spending%20data.%20Participants%20were%20surveyed%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20pilot%2C%20the%20halfway%20point%2C%20the%20end%20of%20the%20pilot%2C%20and%20five%20months%20after%20their%20payments%20ended.%20The%20pilot%20had%20no%20control%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20pilot%20participants%20said%20they%20weren't%20previously%20able%20to%20maintain%20jobs%20or%20school%20attendance%20due%20to%20caregiving%20responsibilities%20at%20home.%20But%2C%20with%20GBI%2C%20many%20participants%20said%20they%20were%20able%20to%20provide%20financial%20support%20to%20their%20grandparents%2C%20parents%2C%20or%20siblings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recognize%20that%2C%20when%20you%20meet%20people%20where%20they're%20at%2C%20they%20actually%20do%20rise%20to%20the%20occasion%2C%26quot%3B%20Asya%20Howlette%2C%20director%20of%20the%20New%20Orleans%20Mayor's%20Office%20of%20Youth%20and%20Families%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParticipants%20also%20had%20a%20statistically%20significant%20increase%20in%20full-time%20employment%3A%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBetween%20the%20beginning%20and%20end%20of%20the%20program%2C%20the%20participants'%20employment%20rate%20increased%20from%206%25%20to%2021%25%2C%20and%20many%20reported%20feeling%20more%20income%20stable.%20Some%20said%20the%20%24350%20gave%20them%20the%20financial%20freedom%20to%20pursue%20training%20programs%20and%20internships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20number%20of%20participants%20who%20had%20a%20housing%20cost%20burden%20exceeding%2050%25%20of%20their%20income%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20considered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-crisis-unaffordable-high-rent-prices-cost-burdened-renters-cities-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheavily%20rent-burdened%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20also%20declined%20by%2015%20percentage%20points%20over%20the%20course%20of%20the%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20a%20month%20likely%20doesn't%20cover%20major%20expenses%2C%20but%20Howlette%20said%20it's%20what%20many%20opportunity%20youth%20need%20to%20get%20by.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20enough%20to%20propel%20you%20into%20wealth%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20enough%20to%20keep%20you%20from%20the%20precipice%20of%20disaster.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e9d58b7b-63f1-45f3-a14a-25be013ae6e6%5C%22%3EParticipants%20struggle%20to%20pay%20bills%20after%20payments%20end%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20employment%20and%20financial%20gains%2C%20many%20of%20the%20benefits%20that%20participants%20felt%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funiversal-basic-income-ubi%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguaranteed