ir%20nominations%20from%20the%20Bahadurgarh%20Assembly%20constituency%20and%20had%20withdrawn%20them%20only%20after%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20had%20intervened.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Baroda%20Assembly%20constituency%2C%20Congress%20leader%20Kapoor%20Singh%20Narwal%20has%20said%20he%20was%20promised%20a%20ticket%20by%20Mr%20Hooda%2C%20but%20it%20was%20given%20to%20Induraj%20Singh%20Narwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20cheated%20the%20people%20of%20the%20constituency%2C%20not%20me.%20I%20will%20take%20a%20call%20on%20contesting%20as%20an%20Independent%20tomorrow.%2C%26quot%3B%20Kapoor%20Singh%20Narwal%20said%2C%20even%20as%20sources%20close%20to%20him%20indicated%20he%20could%20leave%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuoyed%20after%20winning%205%20of%20the%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20hope%20that%20the%20discontent%20in%20the%20party%20does%20not%20hurt%20its%20chances%20of%20dislodging%20the%20BJP%20from%20a%20Hindi%20heartland%20state%20it%20has%20ruled%20since%202014.%20The%20party's%20central%20leadership%20has%20also%20faced%20pushback%20after%20senior%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20pushed%20for%20a%20tie-up%20with%20the%20AAP%20to%20avoid%20the%20division%20of%20votes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20an%20in-principle%20agreement%20regarding%20an%20alliance%20had%20been%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20there%20appears%20to%20be%20a%20stalemate%2C%20with%20the%20AAP%20seeking%2010%20seats%20and%20the%20Congress%20willing%20to%20give%20up%20only%20five%20to%20seven.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Troubles%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20also%20had%20to%20face%20dissent%20from%20its%20leaders%20after%20it%20released%20its%20first%20list%20of%2067%20names%20on%20Wednesday.%20%C2%A0Energy%20Minister%20Ranjit%20Chautala%20and%20MLA%20Lakshman%20Napa%20had%20quit%20the%20party%20over%20the%20past%20few%20days%20after%20bei