s%20and%20the%20lock-in%20effect%20from%20high%20mortgage%20rates%20have%20made%20it%20tough%20to%20buy%20or%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESigns%20of%20life%20in%20the%20market%20include%20the%20fact%20that%20monthly%20mortgage%20payments%20decreased%20last%20month%20for%20the%20first%20time%20since%202020%20with%20mortgage%20rates%20at%20a%2015-month%20low%2C%20according%20to%20Redfin.%20Mortgage%20rates%20are%20slated%20to%20come%20down%20further%20as%20the%20Fed%20begins%20cutting%20interest%20rates%20soon%2C%20giving%20homebuyers%20confidence%20that%20buying%20conditions%20are%20improving.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-home-supply-real-estate-mortgage-lock-in-redfin-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChen%20Zhao%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Redfin's%20research%20head%2C%20is%20confident%20that%20the%20housing%20market%20will%20slowly%20unlock%20over%20the%20next%20year%20as%20rates%20continue%20decreasing%20and%20existing%20homeowners%20start%20selling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20already%20evidence%20of%20this%20happening.%20New%20listings%20are%20up%203.4%25%20year-over-year.%20The%20total%20number%20of%20homes%20for%20sale%20has%20shot%20up%2018%25%20year-over-year.%20And%20Redfin%20economists%20believe%20that%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20NAR%20settlement%2C%20which%20gives%20sellers%20and%20buyers%20more%20negotiating%20power%20over%20realtor%20commissions%2C%20sellers%20might%20be%20more%20willing%20to%20list%20their%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20housing%20markets%20are%20seeing%20this%20effect%20immediately.%20Redfin%20analyzed%20the%2050%20biggest%20US%20metro%20areas%20by%20population%20and%20found%20that%20year-over-year%2C%20new%20listings%20are%20surging%20in%20some%20metros%20quicker%20than%20others.%20Certain%20cities%20in%20California%2C%20Pennsylvania%2C%20and%20Maryland%20posted%20double-digit%20increases%20in%20new%20listings.%20During%20that%20same%20period%2C%20cities%20in%20Georgia%2C%20