urants%20were%20allergy-friendly%2C%20but%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20cigarette%20butts%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20an%20American%20born%20to%20British%20parents.%20My%20husband%20is%20British%20and%20recently%20obtained%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquestions-i-was-asked-in-my-us-citizenship-test-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20citizenship%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20living%20there%20for%2010%20years.%20When%20we%20had%20our%20son%20(who%20also%20has%20dual%20citizenship)%2C%20we%20knew%20we'd%20spend%20significant%20time%20on%20both%20continents.%20However%2C%20the%20pandemic%2C%20finances%2C%20and%20busy%20schedules%20kept%20us%20from%20traveling%20internationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20after%20six%20years%20away%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-tourist-shares-why-you-should-book-flight-to-glasgow-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereturned%20to%20Glasgow%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20visit%20friends%20and%20family.%20We%20knew%20the%20accent%20wouldn't%20be%20a%20surprise%20to%20our%207-year-old.%20His%20dad%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20my%20family%20have%20a%20heavy%20Scottish%20brogue.%20We%20also%20knew%20our%20little%20one%20would%20love%20the%20street%20art%20and%20the%20chocolate.%20But%20after%20being%20away%20for%20so%20long%2C%20a%20few%20things%20did%20surprise%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b332bb64-258f-450f-921e-5dd5e5fcae1c%5C%22%3EPeople%20are%20friendlier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20forgotten%20how%20lovely%20strangers%20can%20be.%20While%20on%20the%20bus%20to%20visit%20my%20grandmother%20in%20her%20new%20house%2C%20the%20driver%20and%20a%20fellow%20passenger%20happily%20helped%20us%20figure%20out%20which%20stop%20to%20take.%20A%20friendly%20ticket%20collector%20on%20the%20train%20paused%20to%20chat%20with%20my%207-year-old%20about%20his%20new%20Lego%20bricks%2C%20and%20locals%20greeted%20us%20with%20smiles%2C%20jokes%2C%20and%20tales%20about%20the%20last%20time%20they'd%20traveled%20to%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20asked%20my%20son%20if%20he%20thought%20the%20people%20in%20Glasgow%20were%20friendlier%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey're%20like%20the%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwedding-anniversary-trip-took-kid-family-vacation-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ein%20Hawaii%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20we%20also%20recently%20traveled%20with%20him.%20I'd%20never%20thought%20of%20it%20that%20way%2C%20but%20he%20might%20be%20right.%20Traveling%20to%20Glasgow%20%3Cem%3Edoes%3C%2Fem%3E%20feel%20similar%20to%20the%20warmth%20(despite%20the%20cold%20temperature)%2C%20generosity%20of%20time%2C%20and%20genuine%20welcoming%20feeling%20you%20experience%20with%20traditional%20Hawaiian%20hospitality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223021%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicole%20Findlay%20with%20her%20husband%20and%20son%20in%20Scotland%20standing%20outside%20near%20a%20big%20stone%20archway.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d893d31d8d2deb96b8c7b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223140%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENicole%20Findlay%20and%20her%20family%20were%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20how%20friendly%20people%20were%20in%20Scotland.%3Cp%3ENicole%20Findlay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fa5c1b6e-1eca-47ed-b859-0676927d2075%5C%22%3EChips%20(french%20fries)%20come%20with%20almost%20every%20meal%2C%20and%20the%20potato%20chip%20(crisp)%20flavors%20are%20better%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20little%20one%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-surprised-my-welsh-kids-when-they-visited-the-us-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epleasantly%20surprised%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20could%20order%20chips%20%E2%80%94%20or%20french%20fries%2C%20to%20Americans%20%E2%80%94%20in%20almost%20every%20restaurant.%20He%20loves%20them%2C%20which%20isn't%20a%20shocker%20because%20most%20people%20do.%20They're%20bigger%20than%20most%20of%20the%20french%20fries%20we%20get%20back%20home%2C%20and%20our%20family%20much%20prefers%20them%20in%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20crisps%20%E2%80%94%20or%20potato%20chips%E2%80%94%20the%20UK's%20also%20got%20America%20beat.%20Our%20favorite%20salty%20snacks%20are%20salt%20and%20vinegar%20and%20cheese%20and%20onion.%20But%20a%20few%20flavors%20were%20new%20to%20me%2C%20like%20haggis%20and%20black%20pepper%2C%20turkey%20and%20stuffing%2C%20and%20beef%20teriyaki%2C%20which%20were%20fun%20to%20try%2C%20and%20equally%20delicious.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6abe88b-2d1a-4b38-aeff-cdd3c20ff1a6%5C%22%3ERestaurants%20were%20more%20allergy-friendly%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalm-springs-california-surprising-things-what-its-like-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elive%20in%20California%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20generally%20a%20great%20place%20to%20live%20if%20you%20have%20food%20allergies.%20But%20Scotland%20took%20it%20to%20a%20whole%20other%20level.%20In%20America%2C%20when%20asking%20about%20allergy%20specifics%20for%20my%20son%2C%20servers%20often%20make%20a%20note%20on%20their%20notepad%20to%20pass%20along%20to%20kitchen%20staff.%20In%20Scotland%2C%20servers%20asked%20us%20if%20we%20had%20allergies%20before%20I%20even%20had%20a%20chance%20to%20inquire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20often%20than%20not%2C%20Scottish%20servers%20passed%20me%20an%20iPad%20(or%20QR%20code)%20with%20detailed%20nutritional%20information%20for%20each%20menu%20item%20so%20that%20I%20could%20see%20the%20specifics%20about%20potentially%20dangerous%20ingredients%20in%20each%20dish.%20My%20child%20felt%20safe%20eating.%20And%20as%20a%20mom%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmade-fun-kids-with-food-allergies-now-mine-has-them-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekid%20with%20food%20allergies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20I%20found%20this%20extremely%20comforting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nicole%20Findlay's%20son%20walking%20down%20the%20street%20looking%20at%20a%20mural%20on%20the%20wall%20of%20a%20man%20holding%20out%20two%20beers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d893fe1d8d2deb96b8c7c4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENicole%20Findlay's%20son%20enjoyed%20his%20time%20in%20Scotland.%3Cp%3ENicole%20Findlay%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228fec5bbd-af69-4609-9fd6-c677b21abed1%5C%22%3EEverywhere%20is%20tap-to-pay%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETap-to-pay%20is%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20seriously%2C%20everywhere.%20Restaurant%20servers%20brought%20card%20machines%20to%20our%20table%2C%20and%20we%20also%20tapped%20to%20pay%20in%20shops%2C%20on%20trains%2C%20buses%2C%20and%20even%20in%20black%20taxis.%20My%20husband%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20much%20this%20banking%20convenience%20has%20grown%20since%20we%20were%20last%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ebc088fc-cb25-4da0-be47-05f0b91cefe6%5C%22%3EWe%20saw%20more%20cigarette%20butts%20and%20disposable%20vapes%20on%20the%20ground%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20surveys%20in%202022%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.scot%2Fpublications%2Fscottish-health-survey-2022-volume-1-main-report%2Fpages%2F11%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E15%25%20of%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Scotland%20said%20they%20smoked%2C%20compared%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftruthinitiative.org%2Fresearch-resources%2Fsmoking-region%2Ftobacco-use-california-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E9.7%25%20of%20adults%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20California.%20My%20kid%2C%20who%20rarely%20sees%20cigarette%20butts%20on%20the%20ground%20where%20we%20live%2C%20got%20a%20kick%20out%20of%20spotting%20so%20many%20%26quot%3Bdangerous%26quot%3B%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20cigarette%20butts%20surprised%20my%20son%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20noticed%20way%20more%20people%20vaping.%20A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.keepscotlandbeautiful.org%2Fmedia%2Fka1itwlf%2Fscottish-litter-survey-2023-final-291123.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20litter%20in%20Scotland%20suggested%20that%20single-use%20vapes%20were%20the%20fastest-growing%20litter%20item%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20we%20loved%20every%20bit%20of%20our%20trip%20to%20Scotland%20and%20can't%20wait%20to%20visit%20again.%20Until%20then%2C%20we'll%20enjoy%20the%20bags%20of%20crisps%20we%20stashed%20in%20our%20luggage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotland-vs-us-family-travel-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725701822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66d894181d8d2deb96b8c839%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotland-vs-us-family-travel-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20family%20has%20dual%20UK%20and%20US%20citizenship%20and%20recently%20returned%20to%20Scotland%20on%20vacation.%20Here's%20what%20surprised%20us%20about%20Glasgow.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Nicole%20Findlay)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fscotland-vs-us-family-travel-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20aviation%20cuts%20losses%20by%20Rs%209%2C077%20cr%20in%20FY24%2C%20Air%20India%20revenue%20up%2024%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725701631000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F27%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1724742744-3171.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2