%20purpose%20was%20served%20by%20executing%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Abdullah%20said%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20remarks%20came%20ahead%20of%20the%20assembly%20polls%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20scheduled%20to%20be%20held%20in%20three%20phases%20on%20September%2018%2C%2025%20and%20October%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20total%20number%20of%2090%20assembly%20constituencies%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20out%20of%20which%207%20seats%20are%20reserved%20for%20SCs%20and%209%20seats%20are%20reserved%20for%20STs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%2C%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%2088.06%20lakh%20eligible%20electors.%20These%20are%20the%20first%20assembly%20elections%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Kashmir%20after%20the%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725700080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpbeqg9lo_omar-abdullah_625x300_07_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fomar-abdullah-says-afzal-gurus-execution-served-no-purpose-bjp-responds-6511311%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20chief%20minister%20Omar%20Abdullah's%20recent%20statement%20that%20the%20execution%20of%20Afzal%20Guru%2C%20convicted%20in%20the%202001%20Parliament%20attack%2C%20did%20not%20serve%20any%20purpose%20has%20drawn%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThrow%20My%20Daughter%2C%20Son-In-Law%20In%20River%20for%20Treachery%26quot%3B%3A%20NCP%20Leader%20To%20Voters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Minister%20of%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20and%20senior%20NCP%20leader%20Dharmaraobaba%20Atram%20has%20urged%20the%20voters%20of%20Aheri%20Assembly%20constituency%20to%20throw%20his%20daughter%20