20pun%20on%20the%20Norwegian%20word%20for%20whale%20--%20hval%20--%20and%20its%20purported%20ties%20to%20Russia%2C%20AFP%20reported.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20carcass%20of%20Hvaldimir%20was%20taken%20to%20a%20local%20branch%20of%20the%20Norwegian%20Veterinary%20Institute%20for%20autopsy.%20Reports%20are%20expected%20in%20three%20weeks%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20witnessing%20Hvaldimir's%20body%2C%20Regina%20Crosby%20Haug%2C%20the%20head%20of%20One%20Whale%2C%20said%20that%20it%20had%20%26quot%3Bmultiple%20bullet%20wounds%20around%20his%20body%26quot%3B.%20The%20organisation%20was%20established%20to%20track%20the%20beluga%2C%20which%20over%20the%20years%20has%20become%20a%20celebrity%20in%20the%20country.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%20a%20statement%2C%20NOAH%20director%20Siri%20Martinsen%20said%20that%20injuries%20on%20Hvaldimir's%20body%20were%20%26quot%3Balarming%20and%20of%20a%20nature%20that%20cannot%20rule%20out%20a%20criminal%20act%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20shocking%26quot%3B.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20beluga%20whale%20was%20estimated%20to%20be%20around%2015%20to%2020%20years%20old%2C%20reports%20said.%20Usually%2C%20a%20beluga%20whale%20can%20survive%20anywhere%20between%2040%20and%2060%20years.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAfter%20finding%20Hvaldimir%20back%20in%202019%2C%20the%20marine%20biologists%20in%20Norway%20removed%20the%20man-made%20harness%2C%20which%20had%20a%20mount%20suited%20for%20an%20action%20camera%20as%20well%20as%20the%20world's%20'Equipment%20St.%20Petersburg'%20printed%20on%20plastic%20clasps%20in%20English.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20Norwegian%20officials%20claimed%20the%20beluga%20whale%20might%20have%20escaped%20an%20enclosure.%20Further%2C%20it%20said%20it%20could%20have%20been%20trained%20by%20the%20Russian%20Navy%20as%20Hvaldimir%20appeared%20to%20be%20accustomed%20to%20humans.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMoscow%20has%20not%20reacted%20to%20these%20speculations.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnMarine%20Mind%2C%20another%20organisation%2C%20which%20was%20tracking%20Hvaldimir's%20movements%2C%20said%20the%20beluga%20whale's%20body%20was%20found%20floating%20in%20the%20water%20at%20around%202%3A30%20PM%20(local%20time)%20on%20August%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725689640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fpvlb0bmo_spy-whale-_625x300_01_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcant-rule-out-criminal-act-russian-spy-beluga-whale-found-dead-in-norway-6510082%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nicknamed%20'Hvaldimir%2C'%20the%20beluga%20whale%20became%20popular%20in%20Norway%20after%20the%20unusual%20harness%20on%20it%20sparked%20speculations%20that%20it%20was%20trained%20as%20a%20spy%20by%20Russia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcant-rule-out-criminal-act-russian-spy-beluga-whale-found-dead-in-norway-6510082%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20the%20fight%20to%20define%20Kamala%20Harris%20will%20shape%20next%20week's%20debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725689401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113144868%2Cimgsize-26284.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhow-the-fight-to-define-kamala-harris-will-shape-next-weeks-debate%2Farticleshow%2F113144738.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113144738.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhow-the-fight-to-define-kamala-harris-will-shape-next-weeks-debate%2Farticleshow%2F113144738.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Brij%20Bhushan's%20%26quot%3BConspiracy%26quot%3B%20Charge%20After%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20Joins%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20has%20claimed%20that%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20joining%20the%20Congress%20and%20getting%20a%20ticket%20to%20contest%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20elections%20is%20proof%20that%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20charges%20and%20the%20wrestlers'%20protest%20were%20a%20conspiracy%20against%20him%20by%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Wrestling%20Federation%20of%20India%20chief%20has%20also%20alleged%20that%20Ms%20Phogat%20violated%20rules%20by%20trying%20out%20for%20two%20different%20weight%20categories%20for%20the%20Olympics%20on%20the%20same%20day%20and%20hinted%20that%20her%20disqualification%20ahead%20of%20the%20final%20bout%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bresult%20given%20by%20god%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%2C%20who%20were%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20wrestlers'%20protests%20against%20Mr%20Singh%20last%20year%2C%20joined%20the%20Congress%20on%20Friday%20and%2C%20hours%20later%2C%20Ms%20Phogat%20was%20announced%20as%20a%20candidate%20from%20the%20Julana%20Assembly%20constituency%20while%20Mr%20Punia%20has%20been%20appointed%20working%20president%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Kisan%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20protests%20began%20on%2018%20January%2C%202023%2C%20I%20had%20said%20on%20day%20one%20that%20it%20is%20not%20a%20protest%20by%20wrestlers%20and%20the%20Congress%20is%20behind%20it.%20Especially%20(Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20Haryana%20chief%20minister)%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%2C%20(his%20son%20and%20MP)%20Deepender%20Hooda%20and%20Priyanka%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi.%20Now%20that%20has%20been%20proven%20true.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20protest%20and%20the%20conspiracy%20against%20me%20had%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20it%20was%20led%20by%20Bhupinder%20Hooda.%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20people%20of%20Haryana%20that%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%2C%20Deepender%20Hooda%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia%20did%20not%20protest%20for%20the%20respect%20of%20the%20girls...%20because%20of%20this%2C%20the%20daughters%20of%20Haryana%20are%20having%20to%20face%20shame.%20The%20Congress%20leaders%20and%20protesters%20are%20responsible%20for%20this.%20They%20used%20the%20daughters%20and%20hurt%20the%20respect%20of%20female%20wrestlers%20for%20political%20reasons.%20The%20script%20was%20written%20by%20the%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20allegations%20and%20the%20protests%2C%20the%20three-time%20BJP%20MP%20had%20been%20denied%20a%20ticket%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20from%20his%20seat%20of%20Kaisergant%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20His%20son%2C%20Karan%20Bhushan%20Singh%2C%20was%20fielded%20instead%20and%20had%20emerged%20victorious.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInsisting%20that%20the%20allegations%20against%20him%20are%20false%20and%20he%20was%20not%20in%20Delhi%20on%20the%20days%20on%20which%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20sexually%20harassing%20wrestlers%2C%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Singh%20said%20that%20the%20court%20will%20give%20its%20ruling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Violated%20Rules'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Phogat%20had%20missed%20out%20on%20what%20would%20have%20been%20at%20least%20a%20silver%20medal%20after%20being%20disqualified%20for%20exceeding%20the%20weight%20limit%20by%20100%20grams%20ahead%20of%20the%20final%20bout%20in%20the%2050%20kg%20freestyle%20wrestling%20event%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%20She%20had%20defeated%20reigning%20gold%20medallist%20Yui%20Susaki%20of%20Japan%20on%20the%20road%20to%20the%20finals%20and%20her%20disqualification%20had%20broken%20a%20billion%20hearts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mr%20Singh%20was%20asked%20about%20this%2C%20he%20pointed%20out%20that%20he%20had%20said%20even%20earlier%20that%20a%20wrestler%20cannot%20give%20his%20or%20her%20weight%20for%20two%20categories%20on%20the%20same%20day%20as%20per%20the%20rules%20of%20governing%20body%20UWW%20(United%20World%20Wrestling).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVinesh%20Phogat%20appeared%20for%20trials%20in%20two%20weight%20categories%20on%20the%20same%20day.%20She%20kept%20the%20trials%20on%20hold%20for%20five%20hours.%20After%20losing%20in%20the%2053%20kg%20category%2010-0%2C%20she%20fought%20in%20the%2050kg%20category.%20Shivani%20Pawar%20was%20winning%205-1%20but%20a%20commotion%20was%20created%20and%20the%20referees%20engaged%20in%20dishonesty%20and%20declared%20Ms%20Phogat%20the%20winner%2C%20and%20the%20result%20for%20this%20was%20given%20by%20God%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlleging%20that%20Ms%20Phogat%20had%20meted%20out%20injustice%20to%20wrestlers%20by%20doing%20what%20she%20had%20done%20at%20the%20trials%2C%20Mr%20Singh%20said%20that%20her%20entry%20into%20the%20Congress%20would%20not%20yield%20dividends%20for%20the%20party%20in%20the%20Haryana%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Dragged%20On%20Road'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20joining%20the%20Congress%20on%20Friday%2C%20Ms%20Phogat%20had%20said%20that%20when%20the%20wrestlers%20were%20%26quot%3Bdragged%20on%20the%20roads%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20protests%2C%20every%20party%20had%20stood%20with%20them%2C%20except%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20for%20supporting%20me%20during%20my%20wrestling%20career%20and%20I%20hope%20I%20live%20up%20to%20their%20expectations.%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20the%20Congress%20because%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20it%20is%20only%20when%20times%20are%20bad%20that%20one%20finds%20out%20who%20is%20standing%20with%20them.%20When%20we%20were%20dragged%20on%20the%20roads%2C%20every%20party%20other%20than%20the%20BJP%20stood%20with%20us%20and%20understood%20our%20pain%20and%20our%20tears...%20I%20am%20very%20proud%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20a%20party%20that%20stands%20up%20against%20misbehaviour%20and%20injustice%20against%20women%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20had%20said%20in%20Hindi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVoting%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Haryana%20for%20the%2090%20Assembly%20seats%20on%20October%205%20and%20counting%20will%20be%20done%20on%20October%208.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20ANI%20inputs)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725688500000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Ffl8er4oo_brij-bhushan-sharan-singh_625x300_13_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushans-conspiracy-charge-after-vinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-join-congress-6510224%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20BJP%20MP%20Brij%20Bhushan%20Sharan%20Singh%20has%20claimed%20that%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20joining%20the%20Congress%20is%20proof%20that%20the%20sexual%20harassment%20charges%20and%20the%20wrestlers'%20protest%20were%20a%20conspiracy%20against%20him%20by%20the%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbrij-bhushans-conspiracy-charge-after-vinesh-phogat-bajrang-punia-join-congress-6510224%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BWon't%20Do%20Politics%20On...%26quot%3B%3A%20Haryana%20BJP%20Chief%20As%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20Joins%20Congress%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20and%20Bajrang%20Punia's%20decision%20to%20join%20Congress%2C%20Haryana%20BJP%20president%20Mohan%20Lal%20Badoli%20said%20that%20players%20are%20the%20pride%20of%20our%20country%20and%20that%20the%20party%20does%20not%20do%20politics%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlayers%20are%20the%20pride%20of%20our%20country%2C%20we%20don't%20do%20politics%20on%20them.%20They%20will%20work%20as%20a%2