d%20the%20country%20for%20over%20a%20millennium%20but%20faces%20the%20same%20issues%20as%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%3A%20a%20rapidly%20ageing%20and%20declining%20population.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHisahito%20is%20the%20nephew%20of%20Japanese%20Emperor%20Naruhito%20and%20is%20second%20in%20line%20to%20the%20throne%20after%20his%20father%20Crown%20Prince%20Akishino%2C%20who%20reached%20adulthood%20in%201985.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BI%20hope%20to%20learn%20more%20through%20each%20and%20every%20experience%2C%20absorbing%20various%20aspects%20and%20growing%20through%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20prince%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20the%20Imperial%20Household%20Agency.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHe%20conveyed%20his%20gratitude%20to%20his%20parents%20and%20sisters%2C%20Mako%20Komuro%2C%20who%20left%20the%20imperial%20family%20after%20getting%20married%2C%20and%20Princess%20Kako.%20He%20also%20shared%20his%20desire%20to%20work%20hard%20for%20his%20future.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20cherish%20my%20remaining%20time%20at%20high%20school%2C%26quot%3B%20Hisahito%20added.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAccording%20to%20the%20agency%2C%20Prince%20Hisahito%20is%20a%20third-year%20student%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Tsukuba's%20Senior%20High%20School%20at%20Otsuka%20in%20Tokyo.%20While%20the%20custom%20is%20to%20hold%20a%20Coming-of-Age%20Ceremony%20and%20a%20press%20conference%20to%20mark%20the%20occasion%2C%20his%20ceremony%20has%20been%20postponed%20to%20the%20spring%20of%202025%2C%20or%20later.%20The%20ceremony%20will%20take%20place%20after%20his%20high%20school%20graduation%20to%20avoid%20interference%20with%20his%20academic%20pursuits.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnHisahito%20is%20the%20youngest%20member%20of%20the%2017-member%2C%20all-adult%20imperial%20family%2C%20which%20only%20has%20four%20men.%20His%20position%20as%20the%20last%20heir%20apparent%20presents%20a%20challenge%20to%20Japanese%20society%2C%20which%20forbids%20women%20from%20taking%20the%20throne.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%201947%20Imperial%20House%20Law%20only%20permits%20a%20man%20to%20ascend%20to%20the%20throne%20and%20requires%20female%20royal%20members%20who%20marry%20commoners%20to%20renounce%20their%20royal%20position.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAside%20from%20Hisahito%20and%20the%20crown%20prince%20Akishino%2C%20Prince%20Hitachi%2C%20the%2088-year-old%20childless%20uncle%20of%20the%20emperor%2C%20is%20the%20only%20other%20successor%20to%20the%20Chrysanthemum%20Throne.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725686580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fakcp51k8_prince-hisahito_625x300_07_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprince-hisahito-becomes-japans-1st-royal-male-to-turn-18-in-40-years-6510031%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prince%20Hisahito%2C%20the%20son%20of%20Crown%20Prince%20Akishino%2C%20turned%2018%20on%20Friday%20and%20joined%20the%20Imperial%20family%20as%20an%20adult.%20With%20this%2C%20Hisahito%20became%20the%20first%20male%20member%20of%20the%20family%20to%20reach%20adulthood%20in%2039%20years%2C%20reported%20Japan%20Times.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fprince-hisahito-becomes-japans-1st-royal-male-to-turn-18-in-40-years-6510031%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Dick%20Cheney%20will%20be%20voting%20for%20Kamala%20Harris'%3A%20Former%20VP%20turns%20his%20back%20on%20Trump%2C%20tells%20daughter%20Liz%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1725686566000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113144007%2Cimgsize-168966.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fdick-cheney-will-be-voting-for-kamala-harris-former-vp-turns-his-back-on-trump-tells-daughter-liz%2Farticleshow%2F113143863.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20a