e-in-ongoing-insolvency-case-124090700161_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCould%20Have%20Stopped%20The%20Split%20%26quot%3B%3A%20Salim%20Khan%20To%20NDTV%20On%20The%20Big%20B%20Factor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fangry-young-men-trailer-launch-a-typical-salman-khan-punch-to-salim-khan-javed-akhars-dialogue-mere-paas-maa-hain-aur-voh-bhi-do-6331293%5C%22%3ESalim%20Khan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshabana-azmi-on-honey-iranis-reaction-to-her-affair-with-javed-akhtar-she-felt-rejected-6026100%5C%22%3EJaved%20Akhtar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20iconic%20screenwriters%20of%20Hindi%20cinema%20revolutionised%20the%20film%20industry%20in%20the%201970s.%20However%2C%20after%20years%20of%20working%20together%2C%20the%20duo%20split%20ways.%20In%20an%20interaction%20with%20NDTV%2C%20Salim%20Khan%20revealed%20that%20his%20%3Cem%3Ejodi%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20Javed%20Akhtar%20might%20have%20lasted%20longer%20if%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%20had%20pacified%20the%20situation.%20Recalling%20the%20time%20when%20Javed%20Akhtar%20told%20him%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20make%20separate%20films%2C%20Salim%20Khan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EJab%20unhone%20mujhse%20kaha%20ki%20mei%20alag%20(films)%20banana%20chahta%20huun%2C%20maine%20kaha%20thik%20hai%2C%20koi%20dikkat%20nahi.%20Kisiko%20zabardasti%20rok%20nahi%20sakte.%20Mujhe%20toh%20abhi%20bhi%20nahi%20malum%20kyun%20alag%20hue.%20Ho%20gaya%20toh%20ho%20gaya.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BWhen%20he%20informed%20me%20that%20he%20wanted%20to%20work%20separately%2C%20I%20said%20okay%2C%20no%20problem.%20You%20can't%20force%20someone%20to%20stay.%20Even%20now%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20why%20we%20separated.%20It%20just%20happened.%5D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalim%20Khan%20said%2C%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CKyun%20alag%20hue%20yeh%20bhi%20kisiko%20pith%20piche%20nahi%20bataye%2C%20uska%20zikar%20hi%20nahi%20kiya.%20Milna-julna%20thha%2C%20baat%20karte%20thhe%2C%20unke%20ghar%20ke%20samne%20se%20hi%20nikalta%20thha%20mai%2C%20roz%20walk%20karta%20thha%2C%20hath%20hilata%20tha%20woh%20bhi%20haath%20hilate%20thhe.%20Joh%20rishta%20hai%20joh%20dosti%20hai%20woh%20thha.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BWhy%20we%20separated%2C%20we%20didn't%20tell%20anyone%2C%20or%20spoke%20behind%20each%20other's%20backs%2C%20or%20even%20mentioned%20it.%20We%20used%20to%20meet%2C%20talk%2C%20and%20I%20would%20pass%20by%20his%20house%20every%20day.%20While%20walking%2C%20I%20would%20wave%2C%20and%20he%20would%20wave%20back.%20The%20friendship%20is%20still%20there.%5D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20the%20break%20of%20Salim%20Khan%20and%20Javed%20Akhtar's%20partnership%20affected%20megastar%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20Salim%20Khan%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ezaroor%20hua%20hoga%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20He%20also%20disclosed%20that%20if%20he%20was%20in%20the%20place%20of%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20he%20would%20have%20acted%20as%20a%20mediator%20and%20stopped%20the%20split.%20Salim%20Khan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3ELekin%20mei%20agar%20hota%20unki%20%5BAmitabh%20Bachchan%5D%20jagah%E2%80%A6%20unko%20%5BJaved%20Akhtar%5D%20yehi%20raye%20deta%C2%A0%20%E2%80%98Maat%20chodo%20accha%20khasa%20tumhari%20ek%20jodi%20hai%2C%20kaam%20kar%20raahe%20ho%20accha%20khasa%20chal%20raha%20kahe%20ke%20liye%20isko%20chodhte%20ho%3F'%20Mai%20hota%20toh%20yeh%20karta.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%5BBut%20if%20I%20were%20in%20his%20%5BAmitabh%20Bachchan's%5D%20place...%20I%20would%20have%20given%20him%20%5BJaved%20Akhtar%5D%20the%20advice%3A%20%E2%80%98Don't%20leave%2C%20you%20have%20a%20great%20partnership%2C%20you're%20doing%20well%2C%20everything's%20going%20fine%2C%20why%20would%20you%20want%20to%20end%20this%3F'%20If%20it%20were%20me%2C%20I%20would%20have%20done%20that.%5D%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalim%20Khan%20added%20that%20although%20he%20often%20meets%20Amitabh%20Bachchan%2C%20they%20do%20not%20talk%20about%20this%20issue.%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBaat%