3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20people%20who%20said%20I%20would%20not%20be%20able%20to%20do%20anything%20in%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krishna%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Bridge%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnable%20to%20watch%20his%20son%20become%20a%20shadow%20of%20his%20former%20self%2C%20Sunil%20enrolled%20Krishna%20in%20a%20badminton%20academy%20in%20Jaipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20bullying%20changed%20my%20son%E2%80%99s%20life%2C%20and%20he%20is%20now%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261402%2Ftokyo-paralympics-india-thums-up-stereotypes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParalympic%20gold%20medallist%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20motivated%20him%20to%20prove%20his%20detractors%20wrong%20and%20he%20did%20that%20in%20style%20by%20winning%20gold%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sunil%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20New%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20pivotal%20things%20happened%20during%20this%20time%3A%20Krishna%20made%20peace%20with%20his%20height%20and%20discovered%20para-badminton.%20When%20Krishna%E2%80%99s%20coach%20explained%20that%20there%20was%20a%20category%20in%20para-badminton%20that%20allowed%20for%20international%20competition%2C%20it%20was%20a%20game-changer%20for%20him.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20never%20looked%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20training%20under%20Gaurav%20Khanna%2C%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20Indian%20para-badminton%20team%20and%20a%20Dronacharya%20awardee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20competing%20internationally%2C%20earning%20a%20bronze%20medal%20at%20the%202018%20Asian%20Para%20Games%20and%20the%20World%20Para%20Badminton%20Championships%20in%202019.%20His%20defining%20moment%20came%20with%20winning%20the%20gold%20medal%20in%20the%20men%E2%80%99s%20singles%20SH6%20category%20at%20the%20Tokyo%202020%20Paralympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20handling%20nerves%20at%20such%20big-stakes%20competitions